# AtomicPtr in std::sync::atomic - Rust

```
#[repr(C, align(8))]pub struct AtomicPtr<T> { /* private fields */ }
```

Expand description

A raw pointer type which can be safely shared between threads.

This type has the same size and bit validity as a `*mut T`.

**Note**: This type is only available on platforms that support atomic loads and stores of pointers. Its size depends on the target pointer‚Äôs size.

